message.body: Going good. Busy busy. How are you?
How's the interview go?? And I just wanted to point out if you had forgotten, SOMEONE has a birthday coming up hahah ;)
Haha. I know!!! The interview didn't happen though. They had to rescheule it and I haven't had another date for it yet. It'll be sometime this week I think. But how're you doing?
Good, same stuff. Dropped off my mom and her friend off at the airport earlier, got the house to myself. So, pahtayyyyyy at mah house hahahah!
I wanted to ask, did you want to do anything for your big day???
Haha. Not really. I know eden said John was going to be down that weekend and mike will be here Friday, but it Saturday.
What's on Saturday? Yea he is! We should plan to do stuff :) did you want to go out for dinner or anything?
Or sorry. Mike won't be here on Saturday. He's going home to jersey for the day. Probably dinner.
Would you want to do dinner on Friday with Seyer? Or do you want him all to yourself and get dinner another day?
Well the following week we go to Disney so probably Friday since I'll see him all week long and we leave on Sunday so I'd prefer to do something on Friday.
Okay, cool! Did you want to go somewhere specific?
Not really. I don't want or need to do anything huge.
Your day, your call hahah ;) I'm good with anything/anywhere! Maybe pick a cuisine first and go from there?
Yeah, I have no idea. Hahaha.
